events.text: [color=#3b80d0][center]Hoagie Roll[/center][/color][br][br]	The hoagie roll has the strange effect of making the wielder start rolling a bunch just because. Luckily the wielder also becomes consistently great at rolling too. [br][br][color=#A5EFAC][center]Left Shift - XBox B - DualShock Circle (On Ground)[/center][/color]
